993
00:39:47,921 --> 00:39:48,922
Come on in.

994
00:39:48,955 --> 00:39:50,657
‐ Hey.
‐ Hi.

995
00:39:50,691 --> 00:39:52,092
What's going on?

996
00:39:52,125 --> 00:39:54,060
Uh..

997
00:39:55,228 --> 00:39:57,430
Might be a bad time, huh?

998
00:39:57,463 --> 00:39:59,399
Yeah. Yeah.
Uh, kind of.

999
00:40:08,775 --> 00:40:10,176
You okay?

1000
00:40:11,878 --> 00:40:13,847
Hey, um..

1001
00:40:13,880 --> 00:40:16,182
Well, I just...wanted to make
